Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.67,0:00:02.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Year 845.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.28,0:00:08.78,Default,,0,0,0,,The Colossal Titan and the Armored Titan appeared out of nowhere.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.14,0:00:13.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Instantly, the walls were shattered, along with the illusory peace of everyday life.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.81,0:00:19.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Mankind abandoned Wall Maria.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.24,0:00:22.50,Default,,0,0,0,,They lost a fifth of their population, and a third of their territory,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.86,0:00:27.12,Default,,0,0,0,,as human activity was pushed back to Wall Rose.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.58,0:00:32.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Then in Year 850, at Trost,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.80,0:00:37.80,Default,,0,0,0,,mankind permitted the Titans to encroach further yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.75,0:00:42.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Eren Jaeger, despite having been eaten by a Titan,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.81,0:00:47.46,Default,,0,0,0,,suddenly emerged from a mysterious Titan's corpse.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.33,0:02:30.29,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll ask you once again! What are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.07,0:02:32.66,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm human!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.00,0:02:38.55,Default,,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.30,0:02:41.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't think badly of me.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.05,0:02:48.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Marco...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.19,0:02:53.14,Default,,0,0,0,,No! I can't fight the Titans anymore!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.14,0:02:53.90,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}What's gotten into you?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.19,0:02:56.19,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}My comrades were devoured right in front of me!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.19,0:03:01.11,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}They got eaten, yet I felt neither hate nor sadness!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.67,0:03:05.54,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}I was just thankful that it wasn't me!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.89,0:03:09.02,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}But I'll be next!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.02,0:03:10.28,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}I get it now!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.28,0:03:16.52,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Our job is to fight until the Titans eat us!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.52,0:03:19.34,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}If I'm just gonna get torn apart anyway, I'd rather—
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.34,0:03:21.34,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Stop! Get a grip, man!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.52,0:03:25.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}It's not just you! Everyone is struggling with fear!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.60,0:03:27.38,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Look at Sasha!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.38,0:03:30.76,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Even after all she's been through, she's still steady.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.55,0:03:37.86,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}My stomach is killing me! May I go to the infirmary?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.90,0:03:41.16,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't take this!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.16,0:03:42.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Stop it!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.22,0:03:47.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Good thing we were sworn to secrecy.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.63,0:03:49.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Everything's already enough of a mess as it is.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.52,0:03:52.18,Default,,0,0,0,,If they found out about Eren...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.88,0:04:01.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Cannon fire?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.56,0:04:03.06,Default,,0,0,0,,But why just one shot?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.06,0:04:04.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Look, smoke!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.68,0:04:06.47,Default,,0,0,0,,It's inside the wall!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.57,0:04:08.85,Default,,0,0,0,,What's that?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.68,0:04:11.48,Default,,0,0,0,,What's going on?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.48,0:04:13.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Was the gate broken?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.44,0:04:15.87,Default,,0,0,0,,That's the most fortified place! It can't be!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.87,0:04:18.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Someone probably just dropped a cannonball.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.26,0:04:22.11,Default,,0,0,0,,But then what's all that smoke?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.49,0:04:24.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Could it be steam from a Titan?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.66,0:04:27.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.58,0:04:29.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.37,0:04:55.18,Default,,0,0,0,,What's going on down there?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.49,0:05:18.04,Default,,0,0,0,,It's alive!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.04,0:05:19.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Commander Felman!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.17,0:05:24.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Look at that!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.86,0:05:26.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Stay back! It's too dangerous!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.68,0:05:29.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Stand by on alert!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.22,0:05:30.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Stand by!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.43,0:05:33.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Load the next round into the cannon!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.47,0:06:07.02,Default,,0,0,0,,What the hell is this?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.73,0:06:12.39,Default,,0,0,0,,I remember hearing the cannon.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.76,0:06:16.62,Default,,0,0,0,,There was an awful noise, then that impact, and this heat...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.62,0:06:19.50,Default,,0,0,0,,We're inside a gigantic skelet—
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.50,0:06:21.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Eren protected us.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.86,0:06:24.40,Default,,0,0,0,,That's all we need to know for now.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.03,0:06:31.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Inside here, even flowers were spared?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.80,0:06:35.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.43,0:06:38.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Eren, what is this?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.50,0:06:39.21,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.46,0:06:41.92,Default,,0,0,0,,But it's evaporating.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.92,0:06:43.58,Default,,0,0,0,,It's just like a Titan's carcass.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.58,0:06:44.71,Default,,0,0,0,,We should get away.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.33,0:06:49.88,Default,,0,0,0,,They're still just watching, waiting to see what happens next.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.88,0:06:53.26,Default,,0,0,0,,The Garrison can't see our movements right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.78,0:06:57.74,Default,,0,0,0,,But eventually, they will attack again.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.90,0:07:03.98,Default,,0,0,0,,After showing them that, I doubt we can talk our way out of this one.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.25,0:07:07.58,Default,,0,0,0,,I did remember one thing, though.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.58,0:07:10.20,Default,,0,0,0,,The basement. The basement of my old house.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.05,0:07:13.62,Default,,0,0,0,,My father said I would understand everything if I went there.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.85,0:07:18.40,Default,,0,0,0,,He's also the reason I'm like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.40,0:07:22.92,Default,,0,0,0,,If I get to that basement, I'll probably find out the truth about Titans too.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.30,0:07:28.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Dammit!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.13,0:07:31.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Why did he keep it a secret?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.59,0:07:36.76,Default,,0,0,0,,It's the intel the Recon Corps has been searching for, at the cost of thousands of lives!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.76,0:07:39.64,Default,,0,0,0,,This is mankind's last hope!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.86,0:07:44.88,Default,,0,0,0,,He was just keeping it locked away in the basement?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.88,0:07:47.65,Default,,0,0,0,,What the hell was he thinking?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.15,0:07:53.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Where has he been these past five years, after he abandoned us—
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.61,0:07:57.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Eren! We've got more pressing concerns right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.71,0:08:02.39,Default,,0,0,0,,The smoke is lifting!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.39,0:08:03.43,Default,,0,0,0,,We'll attack once we can see them!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.43,0:08:04.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's get this over with!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.42,0:08:05.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't move yet!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.12,0:08:19.85,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm... going to go away.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.09,0:08:23.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Where to? How?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.06,0:08:24.75,Default,,0,0,0,,For now, anywhere will do.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.75,0:08:27.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Then I have to get over the wall and find my old basement.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.80,0:08:29.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Before that, I'll need to become a Titan again.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.09,0:08:32.55,Default,,0,0,0,,You can do that?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.55,0:08:35.32,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know how myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.61,0:08:38.20,Default,,0,0,0,,But I think I can.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.20,0:08:42.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Just like you can't explain how you make your arms move.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.92,0:08:47.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Earlier I just focused on blocking the cannon fire.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.38,0:08:52.42,Default,,0,0,0,,That's why my body had no real functionality or durability.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.39,0:08:59.12,Default,,0,0,0,,This time, I'll try something stronger.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.12,0:09:03.18,Default,,0,0,0,,The 15-meter class form I used to kick the shit out of all those Titans!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.18,0:09:06.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Eren, your nose is bleeding.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.76,0:09:11.82,Default,,0,0,0,,You're really pale. Your breathing's heavy too.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.82,0:09:15.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Doing that clearly puts too much strain on your body!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.47,0:09:18.03,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't care if I'm in bad shape right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.04,0:09:20.91,Default,,0,0,0,,I've got two ideas.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.31,0:09:26.17,Default,,0,0,0,,If you two don't try to cover for me, they won't kill you.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.18,0:09:29.54,Default,,0,0,0,,I've caused you enough trouble already.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.51,0:09:33.05,Default,,0,0,0,,From here on out, I'm doing this alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.96,0:09:36.12,Default,,0,0,0,,No! I—
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.12,0:09:37.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Eren.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.24,0:09:39.01,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm coming too.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.01,0:09:39.97,Default,,0,0,0,,No.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.37,0:09:43.52,Default,,0,0,0,,If I can't keep up with you, then don't concern yourself with me.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.79,0:09:47.10,Default,,0,0,0,,But I don't have to do whatever you say either.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.10,0:09:49.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Cut the crap already, for fuck's sake!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.47,0:09:53.03,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm {\i1}not{\i0} your little brother or your kid!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.92,0:10:06.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Captain,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.16,0:10:08.87,Default,,0,0,0,,the next round's almost finished being loaded.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.87,0:10:11.62,Default,,0,0,0,,What's the plan of attack?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.92,0:10:15.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait for my signal!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.03,0:10:16.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.84,0:10:23.23,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}It doesn't seem like the Garrison plans to initiate close combat just yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.23,0:10:28.23,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Mikasa's senses are sharper than a stray cat's, so I'm sure she would've noticed any movement.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.53,0:10:31.96,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Even if they load the next round as quickly as possible,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.96,0:10:34.54,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}it will still take at least 20 more seconds.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.54,0:10:38.86,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Eren wants to act and leave before then.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.84,0:10:46.57,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Why am I remembering that now?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.91,0:10:52.25,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Is it because this is the end for us?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.21,0:10:55.21,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I guess that even in my final moments,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.40,0:10:59.87,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I'm still nothing more than a coward.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.28,0:11:05.64,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}They've helped me out so many times,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.64,0:11:10.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}yet never once was I able to repay them.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.88,0:11:18.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}How could I consider myself an equal to such friends?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.56,0:11:23.32,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}How could I say, "I'm coming too?"
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.32,0:11:25.83,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I'm not even sure if I could keep up with them...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.21,0:11:38.47,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}After this...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.37,0:11:45.68,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}The three of us will never be together again.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.78,0:11:47.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Eren, I—
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.95,0:11:49.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait, Mikasa.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.69,0:11:52.22,Default,,0,0,0,,I said I had {\i1}two{\i0} ideas.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.31,0:11:56.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Armin, I want you to make the final call.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.06,0:12:03.99,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm fully aware how unrealistic this plan is.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.99,0:12:10.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Even so, our best option would be using this Titan power strategically to aid the army.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.96,0:12:13.25,Default,,0,0,0,,I know it sounds insane.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.26,0:12:20.29,Default,,0,0,0,,If you're confident you can convince the Garrison that I'm not a threat,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.25,0:12:24.53,Default,,0,0,0,,then I'll believe in you and stay here.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.53,0:12:26.39,Default,,0,0,0,,That's my second idea.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.28,0:12:31.64,Default,,0,0,0,,If you say you can't do it, then I'll go with my last resort, the option I described earlier.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.53,0:12:35.35,Default,,0,0,0,,You've got 15 seconds to decide.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.12,0:12:41.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Can you do it or not? Either way, I'll respect your opinion.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.98,0:12:51.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Eren... Why would you entrust such an important decision to me?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.56,0:12:57.30,Default,,0,0,0,,No matter how messed up things get, you always figure out the best solution.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.30,0:12:59.75,Default,,0,0,0,,I want to rely on you.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.45,0:13:02.30,Default,,0,0,0,,When have I ever...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.30,0:13:04.33,Default,,0,0,0,,A bunch of times.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.33,0:13:12.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Five years ago, if you hadn't gotten Hannes, Mikasa and I would've been eaten by that Titan.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.79,0:13:25.14,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}It was all in my head...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.86,0:13:31.66,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I had just convinced myself I was a useless burden...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.93,0:13:38.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}They didn't think of me that way at all!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.88,0:13:41.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Armin, we're running out of time.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.86,0:13:45.59,Default,,0,0,0,,The cannon is loaded.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.96,0:13:47.34,Default,,0,0,0,,We can fire at any time.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.09,0:13:57.21,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}The two people I trust more than anyone in the world want to entrust their lives to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.21,0:14:01.61,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}What more evidence could I possibly need?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.85,0:14:07.36,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll convince them.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.36,0:14:11.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Do your best to show them you don't intend to resist.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.63,0:14:22.42,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Something's been troubling me ever since I saw Eren fight as a Titan.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.77,0:14:25.79,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I haven't even sorted out my own \Nthoughts yet, but I've got to do this.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.79,0:14:28.05,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I'll have to think while I speak!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.69,0:14:33.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Stop!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.68,0:14:41.71,Default,,0,0,0,,You finally showed your true colors, monster!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.71,0:14:44.82,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll signal! I'll signal the cannon!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.82,0:14:47.62,Default,,0,0,0,,He isn't the enemy of mankind!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.62,0:14:52.03,Default,,0,0,0,,We're willing to share all the intelligence we've gathered!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.03,0:14:54.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Begging for your lives is useless now!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.27,0:14:58.04,Default,,0,0,0,,He revealed his true form right in front of us! There's nothing left to say!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.04,0:15:01.16,Default,,0,0,0,,If you say he's not an enemy, prove it!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.16,0:15:04.29,Default,,0,0,0,,If you can't do that, I will eliminate the threat!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.80,0:15:06.96,Default,,0,0,0,,There's no need for further proof!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.96,0:15:09.83,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}That's right! It's unnecessary!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.83,0:15:14.49,Default,,0,0,0,,The issue isn't how {\i1}we{\i0} see him!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.49,0:15:15.31,Default,,0,0,0,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.51,0:15:18.31,Default,,0,0,0,,You said everybody saw him!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.31,0:15:21.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Then they must've seen him fighting the Titans too!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.87,0:15:25.54,Default,,0,0,0,,And they must've seen all the Titans ganging up against him!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.78,0:15:32.53,Default,,0,0,0,,The Titans see him as prey, just like the rest of mankind!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.53,0:15:37.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Nothing you say can change that fact!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.64,0:15:43.17,Default,,0,0,0,,That's true...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.17,0:15:44.77,Default,,0,0,0,,A Titan as an ally...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.77,0:15:46.17,Default,,0,0,0,,That can't be...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.14,0:15:57.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Prepare to attack!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.06,0:16:00.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't fall for this clever trap!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.06,0:16:05.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Their actions have always been beyond our comprehension!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.68,0:16:08.86,Default,,0,0,0,,If they can transform into humans and speak our language,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.86,0:16:12.36,Default,,0,0,0,,that's just another way for them to fool us!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.36,0:16:15.20,Default,,0,0,0,,We can't let them do as they please!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.10,0:16:24.64,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}No good... He's stopped thinking entirely...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.64,0:16:26.92,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}He's too scared to think...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.59,0:16:30.11,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Eren! Mikasa!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.32,0:16:46.15,Default,,0,0,0,,As a soldier, I swore to devote my heart to the resurrection of mankind!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.15,0:16:50.61,Default,,0,0,0,,There is no greater glory than dying for that belief!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.80,0:16:55.57,Default,,0,0,0,,If we added his Titan power to the might of our armies,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.57,0:16:59.12,Default,,0,0,0,,it might even be possible to recapture the town!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.12,0:17:03.87,Default,,0,0,0,,For the glory of the human race, I beg you! In my final moments before I die,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.87,0:17:06.94,Default,,0,0,0,,permit me to explain his strategic importance!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.42,0:17:15.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Captain, we should consider wh—
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.14,0:17:16.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Silence!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.07,0:17:21.82,Default,,0,0,0,,No matter how they plead for their lives, they're still rebels!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.82,0:17:23.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Those who break the rules must be eliminated!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.05,0:17:26.77,Default,,0,0,0,,That's what it means to be a soldier!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.40,0:17:32.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Cut it out already.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.92,0:17:38.49,Default,,0,0,0,,You haven't changed. As big as you are, \Nyou've still got the guts of a scared fawn.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.24,0:17:42.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Commander Pixis?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.93,0:17:47.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Can't you see how magnificent his salute is?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.00,0:17:54.92,Default,,0,0,0,,I just arrived, but the situation has already been relayed to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.92,0:17:57.47,Default,,0,0,0,,You go organize the reinforcements.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.47,0:18:02.10,Default,,0,0,0,,I think it'd be worthwhile to hear what they've got to say.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.80,0:18:15.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Based on the Recon Corps' reports, the Titans were predicted to come from the south.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.43,0:18:22.89,Default,,0,0,0,,They originally hit Shiganshina first, in the southern district of Wall Maria.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.89,0:18:28.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Therefore, it was suspected that their next target
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.43,0:18:32.33,Default,,0,0,0,,would be Trost, the southernmost fortified city along Wall Rose.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.49,0:18:39.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Dot Pixis.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.75,0:18:44.97,Default,,0,0,0,,The Commander-in-Chief of the defense of the southern territories, including Trost.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.37,0:18:49.73,Default,,0,0,0,,A man entrusted with complete authority over the key area of mankind's defenses.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.46,0:18:54.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Still haven't seen one...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.07,0:19:00.15,Default,,0,0,0,,I wouldn't mind being eaten, as long as it was by a scorchingly hot lady Titan.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.15,0:19:04.03,Default,,0,0,0,,He's also known as an inveterate eccentric.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.92,0:19:07.66,Default,,0,0,0,,What is the Commander thinking?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.66,0:19:11.68,Default,,0,0,0,,How could he take such dangerous \Nelements up there without any guards?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.68,0:19:17.28,Default,,0,0,0,,The Commander's reasoning is beyond the comprehension of mere men.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.28,0:19:21.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Captain, the troops are in formation.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.59,0:19:23.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Good job.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.08,0:19:33.36,Default,,0,0,0,,I see. So you believe that basement holds all the answers you seek?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.36,0:19:34.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.32,0:19:35.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Will you believe me, sir?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.42,0:19:39.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Since even you yourself can't say for sure,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.17,0:19:43.78,Default,,0,0,0,,let's just say I'll just keep it in mind for now.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.78,0:19:49.12,Default,,0,0,0,,However, you can prove your true \Nintentions by your actions right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.12,0:19:52.54,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll guarantee your safety myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.72,0:19:57.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Cadet Arlert, was it?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.91,0:19:59.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, sir!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.02,0:20:02.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Earlier, you said that by using this "Titan power"
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.60,0:20:06.08,Default,,0,0,0,,we might be able to retake this city.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.08,0:20:11.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you really believe that, or were you just desperate to stay alive?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.12,0:20:15.65,Default,,0,0,0,,It was... both, sir!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.82,0:20:21.42,Default,,0,0,0,,I was trying to say that Eren could take on his Titan form,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.42,0:20:25.92,Default,,0,0,0,,carry that boulder to the wall, and block the gap in the gate.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.69,0:20:29.33,Default,,0,0,0,,The thought just occurred to me...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.58,0:20:36.65,Default,,0,0,0,,But couldn't you look at Eren's power as a chance to turn this situation to our favor?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.25,0:20:43.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Of course, I was also desperate to save our lives...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.95,0:20:47.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Desperate to save...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.60,0:20:50.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Those words are worth more than anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.97,0:21:01.40,Default,,0,0,0,,What do you say, Cadet Jaeger?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.17,0:21:03.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Sir?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.76,0:21:06.70,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Can{\i0} you close the gap?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.27,0:21:11.20,Default,,0,0,0,,I...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.65,0:21:18.67,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm not sure. I don't understand this any more than the rest of you.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.00,0:21:25.57,Default,,0,0,0,,It'd be irresponsible of me to answer as if I knew either way.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.57,0:21:31.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh right, sorry. I asked the wrong question.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.33,0:21:35.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Will you do it or not? Which is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.20,0:22:06.57,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll do it.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.18,0:22:09.85,Default,,0,0,0,,I {\i1}will{\i0} do it.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.85,0:22:15.33,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm not certain I can close the gap, but I'll still do it.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:53.57,0:23:56.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Though at first they turned to run, driven by fear,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:56.28,0:24:00.16,Default,,0,0,0,,in the end the soldiers choose to stay on the battlefield and fight.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:00.58,0:24:02.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Eren makes up his mind
Dialogue: 0,0:24:03.02,0:24:05.22,Default,,0,0,0,,to become hope for everyone.
