Dialogue: 1,0:01:25.29,0:01:27.87,Op TL,,0,0,0,,{\pos(640,25)\blur2\fad(200,200)}Ignore those pigs who ridicule you
Dialogue: 1,0:01:27.59,0:01:30.67,Op TL,,0,0,0,,{\pos(640,25)\blur2\fad(200,200)}for having the will to step over dead bodies and move on
Dialogue: 1,0:01:30.47,0:01:33.39,Op TL,,0,0,0,,{\pos(640,25)\blur2\fad(200,200)}Our complacence as livestock strengthens this false reality
Dialogue: 1,0:01:33.13,0:01:36.11,Op TL,,0,0,0,,{\pos(640,25)\blur2\fad(200,200)}We're as free as starving wolves!
Dialogue: 1,0:01:35.95,0:01:41.51,Op TL,,0,0,0,,{\pos(640,25)\blur2\fad(200,200)}Channel the humiliation of imprisonment into your arrows and begin the resistance
Dialogue: 1,0:01:41.23,0:01:46.73,Op TL,,0,0,0,,{\pos(640,25)\blur2\fad(200,200)}Far beyond the confining walls, you'll slay your prey!
